DESCRIPTION
-----------

upstream:
  1) a copy of the 3.2.7 version of Flowplayer
  2) a copy of the latest pseudostreaming plugin (v3.2.7) from
     http://flowplayer.org/plugins/streaming/pseudostreaming.html
  3) the source of flowplayer.ipad.js (v3.2.2) from
     http://flowplayer.org/plugins/javascript/ipad.html
  4) the source of flowplayer.js (latest available version
     of the source) from http://flowplayer.org/documentation/api/index.html

